          Electronic, Progressive, House, Dubstep | Ministry of Sound

               320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 232:46 | 539 Mb


The Future Sound Of EDM compilation format is one that looks to provide emerging artists with a platform to tread their own individual paths through a bustling EDM scene. Bold, innovative and exciting, expect the series to explore an entirely new, genre-blurring take on EDM that is sure to offer up a whole host of incredible tracklists.
